# Corvette C6 Accessory Product Banners

## Banner Design Requirements

All product category banners for Chevrolet Corvette C6 accessories must follow these specifications:

### Dimensions & Format
- **Size**: 800x430 pixels minimum (or proportionally larger: 1600x860, 2400x1290, 3200x1720)
- **Format**: PNG
- **Color space**: RGB
- **Aspect ratio**: 16:9

### Layout Structure

**Upper Section** (approximately 355px for 800x430 size):
- Premium accessory component centered
- Corvette C6 luxury interior background (dark, professional automotive setting)
- Professional dramatic lighting
- Realistic high-quality automotive product photography
- No text or logos on this area

**Lower Section** (exactly 75px for 800x430 size):
- Solid dark gray/charcoal bar (#3a3a3a to #4a4a4a)
- Smooth, professional appearance
- Reserved for category name text overlay
- Consistent across all banners

### Visual Elements

**Background**:
- Corvette C6 interior (steering wheel, dashboard, carbon fiber, chrome details visible in soft focus)
- Dark luxury automotive setting
- Professional lighting with smooth gradients
- Emphasizes premium quality and craftsmanship

**Accessory Presentation**:
- Centered positioning in upper section
- Clear, detailed visibility of component
- Premium materials clearly visible (leather stitching, carbon fiber texture, chrome polish, etc.)
- Dramatic lighting highlighting key features
- Realistic automotive product photography style

**Styling**:
- No text overlays on the image itself
- No logos or branding on the photo
- Professional, clean aesthetic
- Consistent with luxury automotive branding

### Color & Tone

| Element | Value | Purpose |
|---------|-------|---------|
| Background tone | Dark (#1a1a1a - #2a2a2a) | Luxury, emphasis on product |
| Footer bar | Dark gray (#3a3a3a - #4a4a4a) | Text overlay area, consistency |
| Lighting accent | Warm white/silver | Highlights premium details |
| Overall mood | Dramatic, professional | High-end automotive feel |

### File Naming Convention

```
corvette_accessory_[component_name]_banner.png
```

Examples:
- `corvette_accessory_handbrake_banner.png`
- `corvette_accessory_handbrake_boot_banner.png`
- `corvette_accessory_shift_knob_elongated_banner.png`
- `corvette_accessory_shift_knob_ball_banner.png`

### Consistency Checklist

When creating new banners, verify:

- [ ] Dimensions are 800x430px (or proportionally larger)
- [ ] Bottom 75px is dark gray/charcoal footer bar
- [ ] Footer color matches previous banners (#3a3a3a - #4a4a4a range)
- [ ] Corvette C6 interior visible in background
- [ ] Accessory is centered in upper section
- [ ] Lighting is dramatic and professional
- [ ] Premium details are clearly visible
- [ ] Realistic automotive product photography style
- [ ] No text on the image itself
- [ ] Smooth transition between product area and footer
- [ ] File format is PNG
- [ ] Filename follows convention
- [ ] Consistent styling with other banners

### Component Examples

**Handbrake Assembly**
- Position: Centered, angled view
- Details: Chrome polish, leather stitching visible
- Context: Corvette interior with dashboard/steering wheel in soft focus

**Handbrake Boot Cover**
- Position: Centered, highlighting lower leather portion
- Details: Premium leather texture, decorative stitching, craftsmanship
- Context: Complete ручник assembly to show part relationships

**Shift Knob (Elongated)**
- Position: Centered, upright display
- Details: Carbon fiber texture, leather stitching, gear indicator visible
- Context: Mounted in transmission area with shifter base visible

**Shift Knob (Ball-shaped)**
- Position: Centered, top-down view showing logo
- Details: Carbon fiber body, polished metal collar, leather base
- Context: Corvette gear shifter mechanism partially visible

### Text Overlay Guidelines

The 75px footer bar is reserved for category names. Recommended:
- **Font**: Sans-serif, bold, white or light gray
- **Size**: Proportional to banner size (recommend 16-20px for 800px width)
- **Position**: Centered vertically within the 75px bar
- **Contrast**: Sufficient contrast against #3a3a3a - #4a4a4a background

Example category names:
- "Ручной тормоз Corvette C6"
- "Чехол ручного тормоза"
- "Ручка КПП"
- "Шаровая ручка КПП"

## Creating Consistent Banners

### Standard Process

1. **Define the accessory component** and its key premium features
2. **Research visual reference** - how the component appears on real Corvette C6 vehicles
3. **Specify Corvette interior background** - should show luxury automotive setting
4. **Request 75px footer bar** - dark gray, consistent with other banners
5. **Verify proportions** - 800x430 or larger proportional size
6. **Quality check** - compare footer bar with previous banners

### Common Footer Bar Issue

**Problem**: Footer bars not matching across banners (different colors, heights, textures)

**Solution**: When creating new banners, explicitly reference the exact specifications:
- Height: Exactly 75px
- Color range: #3a3a3a to #4a4a4a
- Style: Smooth, solid, no texture variation
- Compare visually with existing banners after generation

